SUBENT        A1060002   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
BIB                  5         10
REACTION   (1-H-2(HE3,P)2-HE-4,,DA)
SAMPLE     The target was filled with (98.8+-0.5)% pure deuterium.
ERR-ANALYS The standard relative measurement error consists of:
           (ERR-1) Error in the measurement of the yield of the
           reaction protons,
           (ERR-2) Error in the geometrical factor,
           (ERR-3) Error in the number of atoms of the gas target
           (ERR-4) Error in the number of the incident particles.
