SUBENT        A1060003   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
BIB                  5         15
REACTION   (2-HE-3(HE3,2P)2-HE-4,,DA)
SAMPLE     The target was filled with 3He of 100% concentration
           to a pressure of 15-20 mm Hg when working with an
           entrance window of Al2O3 and 30-40 mm Hg when working
           with mica.
ERR-ANALYS The standard relative error of the measurement of the
           angular distributions is on the average 9%. It consists
           of the following:
           (ERR-1) Error in the proton yield of the reaction
            (with allowance for the statistical error);
           (ERR-2) Statistical error of the monitor measurement;
           (ERR-3) Error of normalization against the values of
           the differential cross sections at 90. degr.
STATUS     (TABLE,,Wang Neng-Ming+,J,SNP,3,777,1966) Table I
